### 3. Get feed — should return approved posts for your community
GET {{feedUrl}}/feed
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Get feed — with limit
GET {{feedUrl}}/feed?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Get feed — cursor pagination (paste nextCursor from response above)
@cursor = 1779037433306
GET {{feedUrl}}/feed?cursor={{cursor}}&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Get single post by ID
GET {{feedUrl}}/feed/post/{{postId}}

###

### 7. Get feed — no token (should return 401)
GET {{feedUrl}}/feed

###

### 8. Get feed — user not in any community
### (create a new user without address verification, login, try feed)
### should return 400 "You must verify your address"